UID:mjSL907qgJ1ArsrhY2iNP
SUMMARY:Bingo Loco presents Name That Song
DTSTAMP:20260402T030255Z
DTSTART:20260606T043000Z
DESCRIPTION:Bingo Loco is an interactive stage show which takes the concept
	 of bingo and switches it on its head by turning it into an immersive part
	y that has everyone dancing on tables coupled with lots of booze. The show
	 features hilarious comedian hosts that will have you on the floor laughin
	g\, DJs playing the best of 90s/00 music\, incredible prizes ranging from 
	international holidays to musical instruments or even the odd dildo\, moun
	tains of confetti showers\, on stage dance offs\, immersive light shows\, 
	rave rounds that has everyone on the tables dancing and lots more madness 
	you just cant predict all jammed in between 3 games of Name That Song Bing
	o! We can guarantee you have never been to an event like this before\nThis
	 event is 21 and over. Any ticket holder unable to present valid identific
	ation indicating that they are at least 21 years of age will not be admitt
	ed to this event\, and will not be eligible for a refund. All sales are fi
	nal. There are no refunds unless the event is cancelled or postponed Openi
